# Frontend (TypeScript / React)

- Match existing component and hook patterns; colocate tests as `*.test.ts` / `*.test.tsx`.
- **Tests:** `npx vitest run` (or `npm run test:fast` for repo-wide quick check).
- Styles: prefer Tailwind + DaisyUI; global input in `src/frontend/src/styles/input.css`.

See **[CONTRIBUTING.md](../../CONTRIBUTING.md)** for docstrings (JSDoc on exports), formatting, and lint.
